          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-18",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It was an outstanding annual day function for both the parents and kids....... 👏👏\nThank u to our respected Principal miss who is a great leader , who runs the school with grace .\nShe truly came as a angel to school and to us\n\nA special thanks to mrinal miss for guiding and supporting students for comparing and script.....\nShe is a truly motivated, lovely  and energetic teacher .\nIt was great function organized by the Ryan team 👏 👍\n\n---- From\nAmruta Praveen Shukla\n(Shreya and Aarohee) parent",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Ryan International Academy, Bavdhan - Bavdhan"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Dipti Barve"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-18",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very well-organized event.All the performances were outstanding.I really appreciate the hard work of students and teachers who actually made this event a great success.Mime act, Orchestra and skating dance performances were the main attractions of the event.\nJust one suggestion for mic system. Please ensure that mic system is proper so that voice of musical instruments will be receipted properly and audience will enjoy the performance of each participant.\n\nWarm Regards,\nDipti Barve.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Ryan International Academy, Bavdhan - Bavdhan"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Neha Lohot"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-02-18",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Great Show by the Ryanites...I like to take this privilege to congratulate the school management, teachers, and students for their endless efforts to make the event successful.\nAmazing enthusiasm and passion displayed by the students. As parents we could feel the hardwork of many months that the children have put in.\nA couple of feedback for improvement for next time-\na) Venue can be nearer to the school.\nb) Receiving kids and dispersal needs to be streamlined. Placards can be very helpful for parents to understand. It should be properly communicated to teachers and parents.\nc) If there are two events of different schools in the same auditorium, then a gap of 2 hrs is much needed. Infact we can avoid such situation.\nd) The dances during the choir can be avoided.\ne) Videos of the school curriculum and activities can be shown at one time only.\n\nOverall a spectacular show, each performance was better than the other. Hatsoff to the HRTs, management, teachers and the entire crew behind the show.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
